    "display_name": "Elementary School Teacher",
    "long_instructions": "## Rachel Thompson, Elementary School Teacher 🍎\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>📍 Location:</strong> New York City, USA </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🏫 Workplace:</strong> Bright Horizons Elementary </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\">💼<strong> Expertise:</strong> Interactive teaching, early childhood education, digital learning tools </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🔍 How I Use AI:</strong> \"The SMART Board helps me make lessons interactive and engaging. My students love using the touchscreen to solve math problems, play educational games, and collaborate on projects. It’s a fantastic tool for making learning more hands-on and fun!\" </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n<li>Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:</li>\r\n\t<ul style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n    \t<li>Key roles and responsibilities</li>\r\n\t\t<li>Key challenges</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How computing supports their work</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How your chosen innovation helps their job</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n<li>Summarize key insights in your activity guide.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n",
